{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_06_02",
  "title": "鈴村優 2話 チョコをあげた相手は…",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "優、頼んでおいたバレンタイン曲の\n歌詞の読み込みは順調か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu‚ how's the progress on reading the lyrics for\nthe Valentine's song I asked you about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.358004411
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "それが、自分なりにバレンタインのイメージを\n膨らませてみたんやけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I tried to picture my own image of\nValentine's‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.758004411,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "うちは普通の青春って感じのバレンタインを経験して\nこなかったから、うまくイメージ出来へんねんなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I haven't experienced a typical youthful Valentine's‚\nso I can't quite imagine it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛映画や少女漫画のワンシーンみたいなのばかり\n思い浮かんで、全然リアリティがないんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All that comes to mind are scenes from romance movies and\nGirls' Manga‚ so it feels unrealistic.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.5999998729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.8333330791
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "リアリティのあるバレンタインって\nどないしたら理解出来るんやろ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder how I can understand\na realistic Valentine's…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.4999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.0666664124
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "リアリティを感じるには経験するのが一番だが……\n優はバレンタインにチョコをあげた経験はないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To feel the reality‚ it's best to have the experience…\nHave you ever given chocolates on Valentine's‚ Yu?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.1666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.6666664124
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃあ、うちかて年頃の乙女ですから\n好きな人には毎年チョコをあげてますけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ being a young girl‚\nI do give chocolates to the one I like every year…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.4999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　毎年本命チョコを！？\n好きな人って、相手は一体……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!? Giving chocolate every year!?\n\"The one you like\" means… Who exactly?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.7999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.6999997457
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "あら～？　えらい動揺してはるなぁ\nうちが誰にチョコをあげたか、そんな気になるん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh my~? You seem quite flustered.\nAre you really that curious about who I give chocolates to?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.5999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.0999997457
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに知りたいんか～、しゃあないなぁ～\nうちがチョコをあげた相手は……同じ学校の生徒です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you want to know that badly‚ I suppose I can tell you.\nThe person I give chocolates to… is a student at the same school.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.2333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.9999997457
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "優は芸能コースがある高校に通っているんだよな？\nまさか、相手も芸能人なのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu‚ you attend a school with a celebrity course‚ right?\nCould it be that the person you like is also a celebrity?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.6333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.4666664124
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "そうですよ、最近はテレビにもよう出てはります\n努力家で、人気者なのに全然偉ぶったところがなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right‚ they've been appearing on TV recently.\nThey're hardworking‚ popular‚ down-to-earth‚ and",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.4999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.2999997457
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "ルックスも性格もイケメンやから\n学校にもファンが多いんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "good-looking‚ amazing both in looks and personality.\nThey have many fans even at school.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.9333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "せやけど、うちはにわかファンとはちゃいます\n人気が出るずーっと前からチョコをあげてますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I'm not just a fair-weather fan.\nI've been giving them chocolates long before they became popular.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.3999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.2666664124
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに前から！？　そ、そうだったのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That long!? I-I see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.2666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "優、トリエルは今大切な時期だ。だから、なんと言うか\nアイドルなんだし、しっかり節度を守ってだな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu‚ TRINITYAiLE is in a crucial time now. So‚ how should I put it…\nYou're an idol‚ so make sure to maintain decorum and…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.7666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.4666664124
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "……ふふ、あはははは！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hahaha!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.4666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.6666664124
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "すいません、{user}さんが\nあんまり真面目な顔で言うもんやから……ふふふ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry‚ {user}-san‚\nbut when you say it with such a serious face… Hahaha!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.1999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "まだ分かりませんか？\nうちの本命は、瑠依ちゃんに決まってるやん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't you get it yet?\nMy true Valentine is none other than Rui-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.3999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.1999997457
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "あ……そういうことか……驚かせないでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… I see… Don't startle me like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.1999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ、{user}さんのあわてた顔\n可愛かったですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehehe‚ your flustered expression was\ncute.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.4666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.3999997457
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "せやけど、瑠依ちゃんにチョコをあげた経験は\n新曲のイメージ作りには役立ちそうにないなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But giving chocolate to Rui doesn't seem to help\nwith the new song's image creation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.3333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "もっと恋のときめきを感じられるエピソードが\nあるといいんやけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It would be nice if there were more episodes that\ncould make you feel the excitement of love.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.3666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.1333330791
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_02-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに、一応ダメ元で聞きますけど\nチョコをもらった経験ありますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ I'll ask just in case‚\nbut have you ever received chocolate?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.9333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 164.8999997457
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
