      "text": "うちは相手の印象に残りたい……\nチョコをあげたことをいつまでも覚えていてほしい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'd want to leave a lasting impression on the other person…\nI'd want them to remember that I gave them chocolates for a long time…",
